Imana [Mu kigiriki: Theos] Ni Umutegetsi w'ikirenga w'ijuru n'isi. Ni Umuremyi wa byose 

Abantu bakunze kuyita amazina menshi y'icyubahiro nk' ''Uwiteka, Umwami, Ruhanga, Data, Uhoraho, Isumbabyose, Ishoborabyose, Allah (bisobanura Imana mu Cyarabu)... Gusa muri Bibiliya izina bwite ryayo ni Yehova-Zab83:18;Yer16:21(Risobanura Ituma biba).
